data.description: This STUNNING one-story home is located on a beautiful corner lot with gorgeous rock flowerbeds landscaping & full sprinkler system. Nearly $55K in upgrades throughout. Walk in to an open floor plan with high ceilings and tons of natural light! This move-in ready home features real hardwood floors throughout, carpet in bedrooms only, and custom window treatments in every room! Study with french doors, custom designer paint colors. Lovely kitchen with granite countertops, breakfast bar with large island, stainless appliances, and gas cooking. Recessed lighting & custom chandeliers. Several upgrades to include the Nest thermostat, alarm system, water softener, and rain gutters! Solar panels will reduce your electricity bill and save you hundreds! Spacious backyard with covered patio, perfect for entertaining on hot summer days! The neighborhood features a pool and park playground. Fabulous location.. near shopping, restaurants, 15 minutes to Ft Sam Houston, 20 minutes to Randolph AFB, and easy access to major highways. Welcome Home!
